item.description: Hello! My name is Sherry Zhang and I am a Technology Consultant at Accenture. This is a space where I write about things that I’m passionate about. Projects: Random and fun projects that I enjoy doing in my free time to to be creative and expand my knowledge area. My Gallery: A Google Photos virtual gallery that I use to keep digital copies of my paintings Adventures: As a wanderlust, I love going on spontaneous adventures and learning about the world around me, whether it be finding my way in a busy city or camping in the woods.
